A Ruby port of [monsterid](http://www.splitbrain.org/projects/monsterid).

## Usage

    MonsterID.new('your_seed').save('monster.png')

    MonsterID.new('a_seed').to_data_uri

    MonsterID.new('your_seed').to_s # raw png

